What Buffer is ReadingBuild Week

Reading is a cornerstone of our value to Improve Consistently. Every Buffer teammate can expense any book they want to buy and in any format. We gift every new teammate an e-reader of their choice and all teammates are welcome to expense an unlimited number of e-books, audiobooks, and physical books from any bookstore in the world. These books can be work-related or have nothing to do with work at all (sci-fi is big around here).

We also have a dedicated Slack channel to discuss and connect over our teams shared love of reading.

In the last few months, weve gifted $58,983.70 worth of books for 69 teammates, including the following titles*:
